ster book simon  schuster  isbn  p   joseph fuqua imdb   adams richard traveller a novel alfred a knopf  isbn   skimin robert gray victory st martins press  isbn   turtledove harry how few remain volume  random house inc  isbn  p   when i was on horseback  referencesedit bonekemper edward h iii how robert e lee lost the civil war fredericksburg va sergeant kirklands press  isbn  coddington edwin b the gettysburg campaign a study in command new york scribners  isbn  davis burke jeb stuart the last cavalier new york random house  isbn  eicher john h and david j eicher civil war high commands stanford ca stanford university press  isbn  longacre edward g the cavalry at gettysburg a tactical study of mounted operations during the civil wars pivotal campaign  june– july  lincoln university of nebraska press  isbn  longacre edward g lees cavalrymen a history of the mounted forces of the army of northern virginia mechanicsburg pa stackpole books  isbn  perry thomas d j e b stuarts birthplace the history of the laurel hill farm ararat va laurel hill publishing  isbn  peterson alexander duncan campbell schools across frontiers the story of the international baccalaureate and the united world colleges la salle il open court publishing  isbn  rhea gordon c the battles for spotsylvania court house and the road to yellow tavern may –  baton rouge louisiana state university press  isbn  robertson james i jr stonewall jackson the man the soldier the legend new york simon  schuster macmillan  isbn  salmon john s the official virginia civil war battlefield guide mechanicsburg pa stackpole books  isbn  sears stephen w chancellorsville boston houghton mifflin  isbn x sears stephen w gettysburg boston houghton mifflin  isbn  sifakis stewart who was who in the civil war new york facts on file  isbn  smith derek the gallant dead union  confederate generals killed in the civil war mechanicsburg pa stackpole books  isbn  starr steven the union cavalry in the civil war the war in the east f